Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.71,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要活下去的话不战斗不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.90,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,明明就是叛徒 还说什么不要杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.17,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要 我不想杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.14,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,为了保护前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:59.39,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,为了保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.57,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:08.35,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,从被他打倒的敌人那里 他看到的到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:11.29,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我真的开枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:14.50,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已摧毁敌人 生命反应停止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.28,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,真的吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:22.30,Layzner_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}寻求生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:37.43,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,我是伊基露·卡露拉少尉 我可以进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:38.55,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:42.97,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.83,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我不会介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:49.72,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.12,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,请让我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.34,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,那家伙竟让中尉受那么重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.94,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,少尉 你的意思是要我的指挥权是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.44,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,我想我也有资格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.26,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:06.39,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,我也想出了自己的独特的战术 请准许我出战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:10.57,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,那先让我听你的战法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:16.15,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,面对一架SPT 我们会一直输 就是因为我们的进攻火力不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:17.79,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,好严格的批评
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.73,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,中尉 我是说在古斯特罗大尉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.43,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,请让我帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:26.00,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:31.95,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,用我的座机 再加上两架地面用机器人 从空中和地面夹攻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.23,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,还要用到地面用机器人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.55,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,好处是 可以分散敌人的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:42.03,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,SPT的雷达感应能力 是无法同时顾及地面跟高空的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:47.52,Default_Sub,Eglye,0,0,0,,我的座机从上空攻击 地面则由地面用机器人负责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.56,Default_Sub,Eglye,0,0,0,,由空中和地面两面同时进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.25,Default_Sub,Eglye,0,0,0,,是不是有试试看的价值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:56.56,Default_Sub,Eglye,0,0,0,,你是否有什么不满
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:57.45,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.98,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我答应你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.23,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:10.48,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,那女人 不简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.35,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 别想我会一直包庇你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:28.27,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,通知整备机准备地面用机器人 快进行检查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:49.43,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我 杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:55.26,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我的体内 流着地球人的血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:05:00.33,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,所以 所以我才会杀人是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.01,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,他到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:11.29,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,全交给他一个人已经让他到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.52,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我还有要照顾小孩的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:18.89,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,得想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:25.21,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,他为了保护前辈和自己而杀了人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:28.48,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,这是理所当然的吧 有什么好烦恼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.86,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:35.18,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我认为你这么说也太说不过去了吧 你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:36.82,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.58,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我不知道 不知道他在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.19,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.35,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.80,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,现在大家好好听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:58.45,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大家都知道 他的运输船中还有两架战斗机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:03.39,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你该不会 要叫我们也跟他一起去作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.59,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我们不是军人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.51,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,等一下 听我把话说完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:12.00,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,这是和我们密切相关的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:17.00,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,如果只有生与死 两条路选择的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.99,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我们要自己找活下去的路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:27.11,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,老实说 我看一直让他保护我们 已经让他到了极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.54,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,不要搞错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.37,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,不是让你们用战斗机器人去作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:37.79,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,如果操纵得当的话 或许有一天说不定我们能得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:41.46,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,要学机器人的操纵方法的话 就是要我们去乘坐机器人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:43.61,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那样的话很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:47.43,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我是不想说这种话 也不想去想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.47,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,但这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.72,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,如果他有个万一的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:55.20,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:07:00.78,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我来这是要告诉大家 我们要找自己活下去的路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.73,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,希望你们能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:07.77,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你现在说的 是博士你的个人想法对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.94,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,是的 为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.35,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.26,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不是那家伙说的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.37,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大卫 你该不会想去操纵机器人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.32,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,坐在这等人保护也不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.48,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,谢谢你 大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.17,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,要我们记住 也是命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.06,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,是的 是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.04,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,把他叫来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.82,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士有事找你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:08:01.06,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,他果然还是在烦恼 杀了他自己星球的人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:06.42,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,然后 我们也准备自动加入了战局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.71,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,SPT的操纵方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:11.77,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我有保护这些小孩的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:18.73,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,只要有一点机会的话 我就都会去找那条出路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.92,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我们跟你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.75,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那些追兵对我们来说也是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.57,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要活下去的话 不战斗是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:30.69,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,还有 如果你有个万一的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:34.36,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,谁能去通知即将被侵略的地球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.94,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,能教我们操纵方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.33,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:53.10,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这个头盔里面有微芯片可以跟SPT相通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.60,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,好酷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.88,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,要把我们的头盔改造成这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:02.65,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,只要改造PCM系统的话 应该也能链接上SPT的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:07.29,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,说的简单 要改造大家的帽子的话要花一整晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.41,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那麻烦你明天早上给我咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.00,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,早知道就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.27,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这是通讯回路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:20.62,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,跟刚才的第三回路不一样 是连接在ND接口上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.29,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,亚瑟在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:25.18,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:29.54,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,亚瑟 你好慢啊 你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:30.85,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:36.16,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,今天又要熬夜了对吧 真让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:39.34,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你在说什么 又不是只有你一个人熬夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:42.05,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我有低血压 早上会起不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:43.66,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不要说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.49,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,可以了吗 要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:46.88,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:52.48,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我带了三架SPT 有这架「布鲁迪」还有对面的「贝布鲁」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:52.48,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(720,980)}BULDY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:52.48,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1250,980)}BAYBULL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:55.97,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,还有「雷兹纳」 侦察方法大体都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:55.97,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(530,980)}LAYZNER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.69,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,SPT可以做声呐搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:04.69,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,也就是比如说有敌人的线索 要进行搜索时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.97,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,电脑会分析并去寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.92,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,超简单的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.70,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,可是 实战中光靠那个是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.82,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那样还是太慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.56,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,有谁要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:16.70,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:20.10,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不 先让我试试 因为我年纪最大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:25.12,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,坐好的话 先绑好你的安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.71,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,好了 接下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:32.42,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,再按下上面的圆形按键
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.27,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.08,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不要紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.72,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,接下来要做的是按下左边四方形的按键
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:44.81,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,有两个 要按左边那一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.87,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不过现在不要按
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:53.88,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,机器人就会动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:52.48,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,现在按的话 你的声纹就会被输入到电脑里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:59.18,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,一开始是右边的按键 接下来是左边的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.41,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,只要这两个步骤SPT就会启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:07.63,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,谁去试试贝布鲁 我用雷兹纳来示范
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.79,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,一开始要碰右边的绿色按键
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.24,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,一开始右边 再来是左边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.35,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,这样我也会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:20.00,Default_Sub,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,930)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}布鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:24.34,Default_Sub,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,930)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}贝布鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:27.84,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这个是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.87,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,里面的屏幕是干嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.35,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,正面的是雷达的屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.01,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,上面的是会显示外面情况的屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:44.58,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,椅子上的把手可以操纵左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:49.93,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,食指上的按键是激光炮 拇指上的是导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:53.74,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,基本的设置电脑会全部帮你做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:55.71,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不行 不能乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.71,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,快按那个解除键
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:58.88,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.81,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,左右脚踏板可以控制动力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.41,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,左右两边的脚踏板踩到底会全速上升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.73,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,换一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.27,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,先让我摸熟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.96,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,接下来要显示出影像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:16.06,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这是记在电脑里几小时前的战斗记忆影像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.25,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,战斗记忆影像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.28,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.76,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,有什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.02,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,只是之前的战斗影像而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:29.46,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不 只是有点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:37.97,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,雷达旁的红色灯在闪 那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:39.29,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,是敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:43.96,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我知道拍到的是敌人的影像 我要问的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.26,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那不是记忆影像！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.12,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,现在敌人正接近中！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.76,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,现在？ 不要开玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:03.27,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,雷达反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.15,Default_Sub,Pilot,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.38,Default_Sub,Pilot B,0,0,0,,敌人好像在雷达范围之外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.30,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.38,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,达拉 阿修 通信状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.44,Default_Sub,Ash,0,0,0,,我都听得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.12,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,听得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.18,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,好 作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.40,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,打开第二第三栅门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:32.40,Default_Sub,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(735,930)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}多特尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:36.15,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,接下来要通信时用激光雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:36.86,Default_Sub,Ash,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.28,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,喂 亚瑟 快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.55,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,真是的 我们不管你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:52.31,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.69,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,敌人运输船接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:03.41,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,一架SPT从运输船极速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:06.36,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,一架 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:09.10,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,总之 要设法让它不要靠近这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:25.10,Default_Sub,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,930)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}迪马修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:29.44,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警报 还有18秒跟敌人接触
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.56,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,进行戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.37,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,敌人进入目测范围
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:37.54,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,有热源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:52.72,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.74,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,告诉我它的机种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:59.99,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,SPT-DM-20C 「迪马修」 宇宙用开发机种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:59.99,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(700,980)}DIMAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.20,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,飞行机能是现在SPT中最快的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:04.62,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,有热源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:14.93,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,你想在空中战赢过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.99,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,现在才要开始 那么就打地面战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:20.55,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.36,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,给我下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:35.77,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,还有！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:52.70,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,SPT-DT-25C 地面用「多特尔」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:52.70,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(960,980)}DTOL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.86,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,地面用? 雷达刚才怎么没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:16:00.62,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,为了维持本机安全性 所以侦测地面的速度变慢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.26,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,上面的敌人怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.72,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,它又不见了 把它找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.80,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,12号位置有热源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:17.85,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,上方的敌人用感知系统监控 用热导弹探测器来回避敌人攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:20.76,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这样来不及 把雷达移回上方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:22.12,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,地面上我自己用眼睛找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:28.15,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,达拉 你要吸引雷兹纳的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:28.77,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.95,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,阿修 你去叛徒抢走的运输船那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.40,Default_Sub,Ash,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.22,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不好 他去基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.04,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,虽然是一对三 不过一定要平安的回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.61,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,对空雷达也显示只有一架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:57.75,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那就是从空中和地面夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.65,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,有一架敌机往你们那去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.65,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要离开基地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.50,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不会让你去大家那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:31.72,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,请更改主要攻击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.30,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不行 不可以瞄准致命部位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.04,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,快靠过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.84,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,被他攻击的话我们就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.54,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不要说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.36,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,可是敌人有三架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.76,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,博士 还找不到是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.30,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,一直找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.14,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.42,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,请更改主要攻击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.91,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不行 不要瞄准致命部位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.10,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,要让驾驶员能活命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.34,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,寻找攻击部位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.70,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,锁定攻击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.42,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不行 不能杀了驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.61,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,看得到他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:48.24,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:11.29,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,敌人反应停止 可以击破SPT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.27,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,可以击破SPT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:20.48,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,SPT重新启动中 请快击破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:25.01,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,攻击目标锁定 请快击破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.68,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,剩余时间08秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.00,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,请快击破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.22,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.29,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我不要 我不要杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:44.22,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,明明就是叛徒 还说什么不要杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.62,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要 我受够了 不要再杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.10,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,他想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:56.83,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.30,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,快把武器捡起来 会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.63,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,他想空手拆机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.56,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,笨蛋 想送死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:13.34,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:26.97,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:27.59,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.18,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,他没有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.98,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,没有武器作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.02,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 没人会去救他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:42.11,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,快动 快给我动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:52.00,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,怎么连动都动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.91,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,解除手动操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:55.41,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.70,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这种事你自己做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:58.05,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,已完成
